TOM: Welcome back into the
world of walking, Andy.

01:16.976 --> 01:17.965
LESLIE: Yes.

01:18.044 --> 01:19.375
ANN: I just
wanted to say...

01:19.446 --> 01:21.710
Quiet, everyone!
Ann wants to say something.

01:21.781 --> 01:25.239
I wanted to thank you all
for being so supportive.

01:25.318 --> 01:26.580
