playing a show.

01:39.732 --> 01:40.960
And we want
you all to come.

01:41.034 --> 01:42.058
(GASPS)

01:42.135 --> 01:44.831
It's gonna be a party, so check your
suits at the door. It's gonna get crazy.

01:44.904 --> 01:48.738
Andy's band is really good,
and it's been driving him nuts that he can't play.

01:48.808 --> 01:52.608
