You know,
I don't really like to define it,

02:07.994 --> 02:11.896
but it's like Matchbox
Twenty meets The Fray.

02:11.965 --> 02:13.865
So, rock.

02:13.933 --> 02:15.798
Well, again,
I don't really like to define it.

02:15.869 --> 02:16.927
I totally get
what you mean.

02:17.003 --> 02:18.834
So, I would love to come to this thing.
When is it?

02:18.905 --> 02:20.099
Tonight at 8:00.

02:20.173 --> 02:21.606
No! Tonight?
Yeah.

02:21.674 --> 02:23.608
I can't go.
Why not?

02:23.676 --> 02:25.769
My mom set up
this meeting.

02:25.845 --> 02:27.972
It's like a political
tête-à-tête with a local bigwig.

02:28.047 --> 02:30.572
Leslie, you're not
gonna go? Come on!

02:30.650 --> 02:34.780
