go to the concert!

02:41.494 --> 02:43.724
Come on! Play hooky!
Blow off the meeting.

02:43.796 --> 02:45.263
Oh, I wanna go to
that concert so bad,

02:45.331 --> 02:46.696
but I have to go to the meeting.
I have to go.

02:46.766 --> 02:49.200
But I'll meet up with you guys
after the tête-à-tête, I promise.

02:49.569 --> 02:52.367
(KNOCKING AT DOOR) Hey,
Mark, congratulations.

02:52.438 --> 02:54.303
Oh. Thanks, Nate.
For what?

02:54.374 --> 02:58.242
You got that speed bump thing
taken care of. Finally. Nice work.

02:58.311 --> 03:01.246
Oh, yeah. Yay.

03:01.314 --> 03:04.078
There used to be this huge speed
bump in the center of town.

03:04.150 --> 03:05.174
