lowered 2 inches.

03:11.191 --> 03:15.594
Apparently, what I can achieve in
government can literally be measured.

03:16.496 --> 03:17.690
Hey, Dr. Harris.

03:17.764 --> 03:19.925
Andy's playing
a show tonight,

03:19.999 --> 03:21.227
and we'd love it
if you came by.

03:21.301 --> 03:23.997
I think there's gonna be a good
turnout at Andy's show tonight.

03:24.070 --> 03:27.369
<i>He wrote this new song about what
happened to him called</i> The Pit.

03:27.440 --> 03:30.841
