God Hates Figs,

04:24.931 --> 04:26.728
Department of
Homeland Obscurity,

04:26.799 --> 04:29.233
Flames for Flames,
Muscle Confusion,

04:29.302 --> 04:30.929
Nothing Rhymes with Orange,

04:31.004 --> 04:32.835
then Everything Rhymes
with Orange,

04:32.905 --> 04:34.839
Punch Face Champions,
Rad Wagon,

04:34.907 --> 04:36.670
Puppy Pendulum,
Possum Pendulum,

04:36.743 --> 04:38.540
Penis Pendulum,
Hand Rail Suicide,

04:38.611 --> 04:41.546
Angel Snack, Just the Tip,
